T1  - Attention and Dread: Experimental Evidence on Preferences for Information
AU  - Falk, Armin
AU  - Zimmermann, Florian
Y1  - 2023/12/06
PY  - 2023
DA  - 2024/10/01
N1  - doi: 10.1287/mnsc.2023.4975
